00:08:11,492 --> 00:08:13,703
To the shelter.

37
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:16,080
They're gonna kill him.

38
00:08:23,921 --> 00:08:25,923
Jean? You OK?

39
00:08:26,090 --> 00:08:28,926
Yeah, I'm fine.

40
00:08:29,093 --> 00:08:31,971
It's just a headache.

41
00:08:34,056 --> 00:08:36,434
It's not just a headache, is it?

42
00:08:36,601 --> 00:08:40,396
I wasn't sure how to say this,
but since Liberty Island you've been...

43
00:08:40,563 --> 00:08:43,274
- Scott.
- You've been different.

44
00:08:44,483 --> 00:08:48,196
My telepathy's been off lately.
I can't focus. I hear everything.

45
00:08:48,362 --> 00:08:50,031
Jean, it's not just your telepathy.

46
00:08:50,198 --> 00:08:53,743
